videos.description: Memphis guard Raynere Thornton rises between two Tennessee defenders and finishes the tough layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Thornton goes up strong for Memphis and-1

videos.description: Jordan Bone lofts one up to the rim and Jordan Bowden puts it down with two hands for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Vols go up top for emphatic alley-oop

videos.description: Kyvon Davenport flies in for the block, which leads to Tyler Harris' bucket on the other end.
videos.headline: Davenport's block leads to Memphis transition basket

videos.description: Memphis guard Tyler Harris tries to split defenders, but loses the ball which sets up Tennessee's Jordan Bone for the easy dunk.
videos.headline: Tennessee's steal leads to Bone's transition jam

videos.description: Penny Hardaway explains the confrontational final moments of Memphis' game vs. Tennessee and how Volunteer players had their "fists balled."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Penny: ‘Tennessee’s entire team ran over to fight’) 2018/12/15 ESHEET
